information: The company SOCIETE D'ETUDES DE DIFFUSION DE MATERIEL D'ELEVAGE DE L'OUEST, is a Wholesaler, founded in 1967, which operates in the Agriculture and forestry - machinery and equipment industry. It also operates in the Livestock raising - machinery and equipment, and Gardening and horticulture - machinery and equipment industries. It is based in Mazières En Gatine, France.
